title: Spaghetti with Chilli, Sardines & Oregano | Gordon Ramsay
description:
Here is a way to spice up a typical pasta dish. Gordon prepares toasted breadcrumbs, finely diced chilli, oregano and garlic, and combines it perfectly with tinned sardines to make a super healthy meal packed with protein. Sardines are an incredibly versatile and nutritious ingredient that adds a real unique flavour to this easy-to-prepare dish.
